<!-- WHY US -->
<section id="why">
  <p class="section-label">Why NoVA Haul &amp; Clear</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">What sets us apart</h2>
  <p class="section-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7)">There's no shortage of junk removal trucks in NoVA. Here's what makes us different.</p>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-item">
      <div class="why-num">1</div>
      <div class="why-title">Same-day or next-day</div>
      <div class="why-desc">Most companies book 3–4 days out. We aim to be there the same day or the next morning. Life doesn't wait.</div>
